txt.en: Find crates bound for Dol Amroth, scattered around the town of Tadrent.
Haelam can be found in the village of Tadrent.\n\nReturn to Haelam with the crates.
'You found them? I'm surprised. Maybe you'll be of some help around here, after all.'
Haelam is short-handed and could use some help organizing supplies in Tadrent that are bound for Dol Amroth.

'This town is in chaos! I can't find the crates for an important shipment to Dol Amroth that absolutely must be dispatched the moment the roads are clear!\n\n'If you feel like making yourself useful, why don't you find these crates and bring them to me. And don't come back until you've found them!'
Return to Haelam with the crates
